data.name: LinkLabel1.ToolTip
data.value:
The format string is comprised of comma delimited sections, each section enclosed in brackets. Each section has an index and a format specifier, which are separated with a colon. For example: - Format: {1:d},{2:f} - Text: This number is {1} and the float is {2}!
This following types are allowed: - d/i: Digits/Integer. - x: Hexadecimal. - f: Floating point. - s: String. - c: Character (UTF-8 compatible). - t: Include and translate another Phrases. - N: Player names.
